729800f-a.title: Richmond: Van Duzer Street - Prospect Street
729800f-a.text:
346 Van Duser Street, west side, at the head of
Prospect Street, showing the Steuben Club. On Bromley's 1917
aap it is shown as the Elks Club No. 841.
February 9, 1999
P. L. Sperr
